" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 487px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Estimated unadjusted survival of dialysis patients with and without an implantable cardioverter-defibrillator (ICD)",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 467px; height: 406px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Figure showing probability of survival over time among dialysis patients with a history of sudden cardiac death. At every time point, a higher unadjusted survival is observed in patients with an ICD (green line) compared with those without an ICD (black line).",
