"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Data from Herzog, CA, Li, S, Weinhandl, ED, et al. Survival of dialysis patients after cardiac arrest and the impact of implantable cardioverter defibrillators. Kidney Int 2005; 68:818.",
